data.description:
Beautiful 2 BR/2.5BA townhome in West Knoxville! Located off Lovell Road, this condo has a spacious living room area, dining area and eat in kitchen! Lovely place to call home! Minutes from Oak Ridge, Hardin Valley and quick interstate access to get anywhere! Even the airport!

All Tenants of FYVE are required to be enrolled in one of FYVE Enhanced Renter Services Plans. If no plan has been chosen prior to Lease commencement, you will be automatically enrolled in the FYVE Standard Plan at a monthly rate of $39.00. 

Tenants will be subject to the following charges: 
*$50 monthly pet fee charge per pet when applicable. 
* A one time administration fee of $99. 
*Application fees $40 per applicant. 

Contact us today for your personal tour of this great home - it will NOT last long! 
(All properties are rented as-is) 

Selling or Renting your home with the FYVE Realty, EXCLUSIVE, UNMATCHED, 277 Point, Compound, & Hybrid, Marketing Systems is the answer.
